// ================ DOM ================
const productGrid = document.getElementById('productGrid');
const sortSelect = document.getElementById('sortSelect');
const resetFiltersBtn = document.getElementById('resetFilters');

// Filter state
let activeCategory = null;
let activePriceRange = null;
let selectedBrands = [];
let activeSort = 'relevance';

// ================ Price Ranges ================
const priceRanges = [
  { label: 'Under 4000', min: 0, max: 4000 },
  { label: '2075 - 4150', min: 2075, max: 4150 },
  { label: '4150 - 8300', min: 4150, max: 8300 },
  { label: 'Over 8300', min: 8301, max: Infinity }
];

// ================ Product Card ================
function createProductCard(p) {
  const div = document.createElement('div');
  div.className = 'product-card bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-primary/20 cursor-pointer';
  div.innerHTML = `
    <img src="${p.image}" alt="${escapeHtml(p.name)}" class="product-image w-full h-40 rounded-lg mb-3 object-contain">
    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-sm line-clamp-2">${escapeHtml(p.name)}</p>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">${escapeHtml(p.brand)}</p>
    <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="price-tag text-lg font-bold text-green-600">${p.price.toFixed(2)}</span>
      ${p.originalPrice ? `<span class="text-sm text-gray-500 line-through">${p.originalPrice}</span>` : ''}
      ${p.discount ? `<span class="discount-tag text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">${p.discount}</span>` : ''}
    </div>
    <button class="mt-3 w-full bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium" onclick="openProductDetails(${p.id})">
      View Details
    </button>
  `;
  return div;
}

function displayProducts(list) {
  productGrid.innerHTML = list.length === 0
    ? `<div class="col-span-full text-center py-12">
        <i class="fas fa-search text-4xl text-gray-400 mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700">No products found</h3>
      </div>`
    : '';
  list.forEach(p => productGrid.appendChild(createProductCard(p)));
}

// ================ Categories ================
const uniqueCategories = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.category))];
uniqueCategories.unshift('All Products');

function renderCategoryItem(cat) {
  const li = document.createElement('li');
  li.innerHTML = `<div class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group category-item" data-category="${cat}">
    <div class="bullet"></div>
    <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary font-medium">${cat}</span>
  </div>`;
  return li;
}

// ================ Price Range ================
function renderPriceItem(r) {
  const li = document.createElement('li');
  li.innerHTML = `<div class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group price-range-item" data-min="${r.min}" data-max="${r.max}">
    <div class="bullet"></div>
    <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary font-medium">${r.label}</span>
  </div>`;
  return li;
}

// ================ Brands ================
const uniqueBrands = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.brand))];

function renderBrandItem(b) {
  const li = document.createElement('li');
  li.innerHTML = `<label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
    <input type="checkbox" value="${b}" class="brand-checkbox hidden">
    <div class="bullet"></div>
    <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary">${b}</span>
  </label>`;
  return li;
}

// ================ Initialize Filters (Once) ================
function initializeFilters() {
  const catDesktop = document.getElementById('categoryListDesktop');
  const catMobile = document.getElementById('categoryList');
  const priceDesktop = document.getElementById('priceRangeListDesktop');
  const priceMobile = document.getElementById('priceRangeList');
  const brandDesktop = document.getElementById('brandListDesktop');
  const brandMobile = document.getElementById('brandList');

  // Clear
  [catDesktop, catMobile, priceDesktop, priceMobile, brandDesktop, brandMobile].forEach(el => el.innerHTML = '');

  // Populate
  uniqueCategories.forEach(cat => {
    catDesktop.appendChild(renderCategoryItem(cat));
    catMobile.appendChild(renderCategoryItem(cat));
  });

  priceRanges.forEach(r => {
    priceDesktop.appendChild(renderPriceItem(r));
    priceMobile.appendChild(renderPriceItem(r));
  });

  uniqueBrands.forEach(b => {
    brandDesktop.appendChild(renderBrandItem(b));
    brandMobile.appendChild(renderBrandItem(b));
  });
}

// ================ Event Listeners ================
function setupEventListeners() {
  // Category
  document.querySelectorAll('.category-item').forEach(item => {
    item.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const cat = item.dataset.category;
      activeCategory = activeCategory === cat ? null : cat;
      updateCategoryUI();
      applyFilters();
      if (window.innerWidth < 768) closeMobileDropdown('category');
    });
  });

  // Price
  document.querySelectorAll('.price-range-item').forEach(item => {
    item.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const min = +item.dataset.min;
      const max = item.dataset.max === 'Infinity' ? Infinity : +item.dataset.max;
      const range = { min, max };
      activePriceRange = JSON.stringify(activePriceRange) === JSON.stringify(range) ? null : range;
      updatePriceRangeUI();
      applyFilters();
      if (window.innerWidth < 768) closeMobileDropdown('price');
    });
  });

  // Brands
  document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox').forEach(cb => {
    cb.addEventListener('change', () => {
      selectedBrands = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox:checked')).map(c => c.value);
      applyFilters();
    });
  });

  // Sorting
  sortSelect.addEventListener('change', () => {
    activeSort = sortSelect.value;
    applyFilters();
  });

  // Reset
  resetFiltersBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    activeCategory = activePriceRange = null;
    selectedBrands = [];
    activeSort = 'relevance';
    sortSelect.value = 'relevance';
    document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox').forEach(cb => cb.checked = false);
    updateCategoryUI();
    updatePriceRangeUI();
    applyFilters();

    Toastify({
      text: "Filters reset successfully!",
      duration: 3000,
      gravity: "top",
      position: "right",
      backgroundColor: "#10b981",
      stopOnFocus: true,
    }).showToast();
  });
}

// ================ UI Updates ================
function updateCategoryUI() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.category-item .bullet').forEach(b => {
    b.classList.toggle('selected', b.parentElement.dataset.category === activeCategory);
  });
}

function updatePriceRangeUI() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.price-range-item .bullet').forEach(b => {
    const p = b.parentElement;
    const min = +p.dataset.min;
    const max = p.dataset.max === 'Infinity' ? Infinity : +p.dataset.max;
    b.classList.toggle('selected', activePriceRange?.min === min && activePriceRange?.max === max);
  });
}

// ================ Filters ================
function applyFilters() {
  let list = [...products];
  if (activeCategory && activeCategory !== 'All Products') {
    list = list.filter(p => p.category === activeCategory);
  }
  if (activePriceRange) {
    list = list.filter(p => p.price >= activePriceRange.min && p.price <= activePriceRange.max);
  }
  if (selectedBrands.length) {
    list = list.filter(p => selectedBrands.includes(p.brand));
  }
  if (activeSort === 'price-low') list.sort((a, b) => a.price - b.price);
  if (activeSort === 'price-high') list.sort((a, b) => b.price - a.price);
  displayProducts(list);
}

// ================ Mobile Dropdown ================
function initializeMobileDropdowns() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-header').forEach(header => {
    header.addEventListener('click', function () {
      const content = this.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
      const icon = this.querySelector('i');
      content.classList.toggle('open');
      icon.classList.toggle('fa-chevron-down');
      icon.classList.toggle('fa-chevron-up');

      document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-header').forEach(other => {
        if (other !== this) {
          const oc = other.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
          const oi = other.querySelector('i');
          oc.classList.remove('open');
          oi.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
          oi.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
        }
      });
    });
  });
}

function closeMobileDropdown(type) {
  const dd = document.querySelector(`.filter-dropdown[data-type="${type}"]`);
  const content = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
  const icon = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-header i');
  content.classList.remove('open');
  icon.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
  icon.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
}

window.toggleBrandList = () => {
  const list = document.getElementById('brandListDesktop');
  list.classList.toggle('hidden');
  document.getElementById('brandToggle').textContent = list.classList.contains('hidden') ? '+' : '';
};

function escapeHtml(str) {
  return String(str).replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;').replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
}

Minor Issues & Fixes

1. Event Listeners Attached Before DOM Elements Exist

setupEventListeners() is called before initializeFilters() populates the DOM.

Problem:

js
document.querySelectorAll('.category-item') // returns empty NodeList

Fix: Move setupEventListeners() after initializeFilters() inside initializePage():

js
function initializePage() {
  initializeFilters();           // Populates DOM
  displayProducts(products);
  updateCategoryUI();
  updatePriceRangeUI();
  initializeMobileDropdowns();
  setupEventListeners();        // Now works!
}

2. Brand Checkbox Event Listeners Not Re-Attached After DOM Rebuild

You're re-rendering brand lists in initializeFilters(), but event listeners are lost.

Fix: Use event delegation instead of attaching to each checkbox.

Replace this:

js
document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox').forEach(cb => {
  cb.addEventListener('change', ...);
});

With event delegation on a parent:

js
// Add this in setupEventListeners()
document.getElementById('brandListDesktop').addEventListener('change', (e) => {
  if (e.target.classList.contains('brand-checkbox')) {
    selectedBrands = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox:checked')).map(c => c.value);
    applyFilters();
  }
});

document.getElementById('brandList').addEventListener('change', (e) => {
  if (e.target.classList.contains('brand-checkbox')) {
    selectedBrands = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox:checked')).map(c => c.value);
    applyFilters();
  }
});

And remove the old .forEach loop.

3. Price Range Filtering Uses Wrong Values

Your products have prices like 45.80, but priceRanges go up to 8300+.

Issue: No product exceeds 100 higher ranges will never match.

Fix: Update priceRanges to realistic values:

js
const priceRanges = [
  { label: 'Under 50', min: 0, max: 50 },
  { label: '50 - 100', min: 50, max: 100 },
  { label: '100 - 200', min: 100, max: 200 },
  { label: 'Over 200', min: 201, max: Infinity }
];

4. Missing Fallback Images

Some images use via.placeholder.com, others Pinterest URLs (may break).

Fix: Add fallback with onerror:

js
<img src="${p.image}" 
     onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/300x200?text=No+Image'" 
     alt="..." class="...">

Update in createProductCard():

js
<img src="${p.image}" 
     onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/eeeeee/999999?text=No+Image'" 
     alt="${escapeHtml(p.name)}" 
     class="product-image w-full h-40 rounded-lg mb-3 object-contain">

5. Hero Banner Image Too Large / Slow

Pinterest 1200x image slow mobile load.

Fix: Use optimized image or WebP:

html
style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757148-5c350d0d3c56?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');"

Or add loading="lazy" if using <img>.

6. Sort Select Width Issue

html
<select id="sortSelect" class="w-57 ...">

w-57 Tailwind doesn't have w-57. Use w-56 or w-64.

Fix:

html
class="w-56 md:w-64 ..."

7. Mobile Grid Classes Overridden

You have:

html
grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4

But in @media (max-width: 767px) you override with:

css
.grid-cols-1 { grid-template-columns: repeat(1, minmax(0, 1fr)); }

This breaks Tailwind's sm:, lg: classes.

Remove these lines from <style>:

css
.grid-cols-1 { ... }
.sm\:grid-cols-2 { ... }
...

Keep only the Tailwind classes in HTML they already handle responsiveness.

         <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Try adjusting your filters</p>
       </div>`
    : '';

// ================ Categories & Brands ================
const uniqueCategories = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.category))];
uniqueCategories.unshift('All Products');
const uniqueBrands = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.brand))];

function renderCategoryItem(cat) {
  const li = document.createElement('li');
  li.innerHTML = `<div class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group category-item" data-category="${cat}">
    <div class="bullet"></div>
    <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary font-medium">${cat}</span>
  </div>`;
  return li;
}

function renderPriceItem(r) {
  const li = document.createElement('li');
  li.innerHTML = `<div class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group price-range-item" data-min="${r.min}" data-max="${r.max}">
    <div class="bullet"></div>
    <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary font-medium">${r.label}</span>
  </div>`;
  return li;
}

function renderBrandItem(b) {
  const li = document.createElement('li');
  li.innerHTML = `<label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
    <input type="checkbox" value="${b}" class="brand-checkbox hidden">
    <div class="bullet"></div>
    <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary">${b}</span>
  </label>`;
  return li;
}

// ================ Initialize Filters ================
function initializeFilters() {
  const catDesktop = document.getElementById('categoryListDesktop');
  const catMobile = document.getElementById('categoryList');
  const priceDesktop = document.getElementById('priceRangeListDesktop');
  const priceMobile = document.getElementById('priceRangeList');
  const brandDesktop = document.getElementById('brandListDesktop');
  const brandMobile = document.getElementById('brandList');

  [catDesktop, catMobile, priceDesktop, priceMobile, brandDesktop, brandMobile].forEach(el => el.innerHTML = '');

  uniqueCategories.forEach(cat => {
    catDesktop.appendChild(renderCategoryItem(cat));
    catMobile.appendChild(renderCategoryItem(cat));
  });

  priceRanges.forEach(r => {
    priceDesktop.appendChild(renderPriceItem(r));
    priceMobile.appendChild(renderPriceItem(r));
  });

  uniqueBrands.forEach(b => {
    brandDesktop.appendChild(renderBrandItem(b));
    brandMobile.appendChild(renderBrandItem(b));
  });
}

// ================ Event Listeners (Delegation) ================
function setupEventListeners() {
  // Categories
  document.addEventListener('click', e => {
    if (e.target.closest('.category-item')) {
      const item = e.target.closest('.category-item');
      const cat = item.dataset.category;
      activeCategory = activeCategory === cat ? null : cat;
      updateCategoryUI();
      applyFilters();
      if (window.innerWidth < 768) closeMobileDropdown('category');
    }
  });

  // Price Range
  document.addEventListener('click', e => {
    if (e.target.closest('.price-range-item')) {
      const item = e.target.closest('.price-range-item');
      const min = +item.dataset.min;
      const max = item.dataset.max === 'Infinity' ? Infinity : +item.dataset.max;
      const range = { min, max };
      activePriceRange = JSON.stringify(activePriceRange) === JSON.stringify(range) ? null : range;
      updatePriceRangeUI();
      applyFilters();
      if (window.innerWidth < 768) closeMobileDropdown('price');
    }
  });

  // Brands (Delegation)
  ['brandListDesktop', 'brandList'].forEach(id => {
    document.getElementById(id).addEventListener('change', e => {
      if (e.target.classList.contains('brand-checkbox')) {
        selectedBrands = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox:checked')).map(c => c.value);
        applyFilters();
      }
    });
  });

  // Sorting
  sortSelect.addEventListener('change', () => {
    activeSort = sortSelect.value;
    applyFilters();
  });

  // Reset
  resetFiltersBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    activeCategory = activePriceRange = null;
    selectedBrands = [];
    activeSort = 'relevance';
    sortSelect.value = 'relevance';
    document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox').forEach(cb => cb.checked = false);
    updateCategoryUI();
    updatePriceRangeUI();
    applyFilters();

    Toastify({
      text: "Filters reset successfully!",
      duration: 3000,
      gravity: "top",
      position: "right",
      backgroundColor: "#10b981",
      stopOnFocus: true,
    }).showToast();
  });
}

// ================ UI Updates ================
function updateCategoryUI() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.category-item .bullet').forEach(b => {
    b.classList.toggle('selected', b.parentElement.dataset.category === activeCategory);
  });
}

function updatePriceRangeUI() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.price-range-item .bullet').forEach(b => {
    const p = b.parentElement;
    const min = +p.dataset.min;
    const max = p.dataset.max === 'Infinity' ? Infinity : +p.dataset.max;
    b.classList.toggle('selected', activePriceRange?.min === min && activePriceRange?.max === max);
  });
}

// ================ Filters ================
function applyFilters() {
  let list = [...products];
  if (activeCategory && activeCategory !== 'All Products') {
    list = list.filter(p => p.category === activeCategory);
  }
  if (activePriceRange) {
    list = list.filter(p => p.price >= activePriceRange.min && p.price <= activePriceRange.max);
  }
  if (selectedBrands.length) {
    list = list.filter(p => selectedBrands.includes(p.brand));
  }
  if (activeSort === 'price-low') list.sort((a, b) => a.price - b.price);
  if (activeSort === 'price-high') list.sort((a, b) => b.price - a.price);
  displayProducts(list);
}

// ================ Mobile Dropdown ================
function initializeMobileDropdowns() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-header').forEach(header => {
    header.addEventListener('click', function () {
      const content = this.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
      const icon = this.querySelector('i');
      content.classList.toggle('open');
      icon.classList.toggle('fa-chevron-down');
      icon.classList.toggle('fa-chevron-up');

      document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-header').forEach(other => {
        if (other !== this) {
          const oc = other.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
          const oi = other.querySelector('i');
          oc.classList.remove('open');
          oi.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
          oi.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
        }
      });
    });
  });
}

function closeMobileDropdown(type) {
  const dd = document.querySelector(`.filter-dropdown[data-type="${type}"]`);
  if (dd) {
    const content = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
    const icon = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-header i');
    content.classList.remove('open');
    icon.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
    icon.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
  }
}

window.toggleBrandList = () => {
  const list = document.getElementById('brandListDesktop');
  list.classList.toggle('hidden');
  document.getElementById('brandToggle').textContent = list.classList.contains('hidden') ? '+' : '';
};

// ================ Utils ================
function escapeHtml(str) {
  return String(str).replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;').replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
}

window.openProductDetails = (id) => {
  window.location.href = `/productdetails.html?id=${id}`;
};

// ================ Init ================
function initializePage() {
  initializeFilters();
  displayProducts(products);
  updateCategoryUI();
  updatePriceRangeUI();
  initializeMobileDropdowns();
  setupEventListeners();
}

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initializePage);

// Scroll to Top
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  document.querySelector('.go-top-btn').classList.toggle('visible', window.scrollY > 300);
});

    // ================ Product Card ================
    function createProductCard(p) {
      const div = document.createElement('div');
      div.className = 'product-card bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-primary/20 cursor-pointer';
      div.innerHTML = `
        <img src="${p.image}" alt="${escapeHtml(p.name)}" class="product-image w-full h-40 rounded-lg mb-3 object-contain">
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 text-sm line-clamp-2">${escapeHtml(p.name)}</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">${escapeHtml(p.brand)}</p>
        <div class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="price-tag text-lg font-bold text-green-600">${p.price.toFixed(2)}</span>
          ${p.originalPrice ? `<span class="text-sm text-gray-500 line-through">${p.originalPrice}</span>` : ''}
          ${p.discount ? `<span class="discount-tag text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">${p.discount}</span>` : ''}
        </div>
        <button class="mt-3 w-full bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium" onclick="openProductDetails(${p.id})">
          View Details
        </button>
      `;
      return div;
    }

    function displayProducts(list) {
      productGrid.innerHTML = list.length === 0
        ? `<div class="col-span-full text-center py-12">
            <i class="fas fa-search text-4xl text-gray-400 mb-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-700">No products found</h3>
          </div>`
        : '';
      list.forEach(p => productGrid.appendChild(createProductCard(p)));
    }

    // ================ Categories ================
    const uniqueCategories = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.category))];
    uniqueCategories.unshift('All Products');

    function renderCategoryItem(cat) {
      const li = document.createElement('li');
      li.innerHTML = `<div class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group category-item" data-category="${cat}">
        <div class="bullet"></div>
        <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary font-medium">${cat}</span>
      </div>`;
      return li;
    }

    // ================ Price Range ================
    function renderPriceItem(r) {
      const li = document.createElement('li');
      li.innerHTML = `<div class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group price-range-item" data-min="${r.min}" data-max="${r.max}">
        <div class="bullet"></div>
        <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary font-medium">${r.label}</span>
      </div>`;
      return li;
    }

    // ================ Brands ================
    const uniqueBrands = [...new Set(products.map(p => p.brand))];

    function renderBrandItem(b) {
      const li = document.createElement('li');
      li.innerHTML = `<label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer group">
        <input type="checkbox" value="${b}" class="brand-checkbox hidden">
        <div class="bullet"></div>
        <span class="text-gray-700 group-hover:text-primary">${b}</span>
      </label>`;
      return li;
    }

    // ================ Initialize Filters (Once) ================
    function initializeFilters() {
      const catDesktop = document.getElementById('categoryListDesktop');
      const catMobile = document.getElementById('categoryList');
      const priceDesktop = document.getElementById('priceRangeListDesktop');
      const priceMobile = document.getElementById('priceRangeList');
      const brandDesktop = document.getElementById('brandListDesktop');
      const brandMobile = document.getElementById('brandList');

      // Clear
      [catDesktop, catMobile, priceDesktop, priceMobile, brandDesktop, brandMobile].forEach(el => el.innerHTML = '');

      // Populate
      uniqueCategories.forEach(cat => {
        catDesktop.appendChild(renderCategoryItem(cat));
        catMobile.appendChild(renderCategoryItem(cat));
      });

      priceRanges.forEach(r => {
        priceDesktop.appendChild(renderPriceItem(r));
        priceMobile.appendChild(renderPriceItem(r));
      });

      uniqueBrands.forEach(b => {
        brandDesktop.appendChild(renderBrandItem(b));
        brandMobile.appendChild(renderBrandItem(b));
      });
    }

    // ================ Event Listeners ================
    function setupEventListeners() {
      // Category
      document.querySelectorAll('.category-item').forEach(item => {
        item.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const cat = item.dataset.category;
          activeCategory = activeCategory === cat ? null : cat;
          updateCategoryUI();
          applyFilters();
          if (window.innerWidth < 768) closeMobileDropdown('category');
        });
      });

      // Price
      document.querySelectorAll('.price-range-item').forEach(item => {
        item.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const min = +item.dataset.min;
          const max = item.dataset.max === 'Infinity' ? Infinity : +item.dataset.max;
          const range = { min, max };
          activePriceRange = JSON.stringify(activePriceRange) === JSON.stringify(range) ? null : range;
          updatePriceRangeUI();
          applyFilters();
          if (window.innerWidth < 768) closeMobileDropdown('price');
        });
      });

      // Brands
      document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox').forEach(cb => {
        cb.addEventListener('change', () => {
          selectedBrands = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox:checked')).map(c => c.value);
          applyFilters();
        });
      });

      // Sorting
      sortSelect.addEventListener('change', () => {
        activeSort = sortSelect.value;
        applyFilters();
      });

      // Reset
      resetFiltersBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        activeCategory = activePriceRange = null;
        selectedBrands = [];
        activeSort = 'relevance';
        sortSelect.value = 'relevance';
        document.querySelectorAll('.brand-checkbox').forEach(cb => cb.checked = false);
        updateCategoryUI();
        updatePriceRangeUI();
        applyFilters();

        Toastify({
          text: "Filters reset successfully!",
          duration: 3000,
          gravity: "top",
          position: "right",
          backgroundColor: "#10b981",
          stopOnFocus: true,
        }).showToast();
      });
    }

    // ================ UI Updates ================
    function updateCategoryUI() {
      document.querySelectorAll('.category-item .bullet').forEach(b => {
        b.classList.toggle('selected', b.parentElement.dataset.category === activeCategory);
      });
    }

    function updatePriceRangeUI() {
      document.querySelectorAll('.price-range-item .bullet').forEach(b => {
        const p = b.parentElement;
        const min = +p.dataset.min;
        const max = p.dataset.max === 'Infinity' ? Infinity : +p.dataset.max;
        b.classList.toggle('selected', activePriceRange?.min === min && activePriceRange?.max === max);
      });
    }

    // ================ Filters ================
    function applyFilters() {
      let list = [...products];
      if (activeCategory && activeCategory !== 'All Products') {
        list = list.filter(p => p.category === activeCategory);
      }
      if (activePriceRange) {
        list = list.filter(p => p.price >= activePriceRange.min && p.price <= activePriceRange.max);
      }
      if (selectedBrands.length) {
        list = list.filter(p => selectedBrands.includes(p.brand));
      }
      if (activeSort === 'price-low') list.sort((a, b) => a.price - b.price);
      if (activeSort === 'price-high') list.sort((a, b) => b.price - a.price);
      displayProducts(list);
    }

    // ================ Mobile Dropdown ================
    function initializeMobileDropdowns() {
      document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-header').forEach(header => {
        header.addEventListener('click', function () {
          const content = this.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
          const icon = this.querySelector('i');
          content.classList.toggle('open');
          icon.classList.toggle('fa-chevron-down');
          icon.classList.toggle('fa-chevron-up');

          document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-header').forEach(other => {
            if (other !== this) {
              const oc = other.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
              const oi = other.querySelector('i');
              oc.classList.remove('open');
              oi.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
              oi.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
            }
          });
        });
      });
    }

    function closeMobileDropdown(type) {
      const dd = document.querySelector(`.filter-dropdown[data-type="${type}"]`);
      const content = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
      const icon = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-header i');
      content.classList.remove('open');
      icon.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
      icon.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
    }

    window.toggleBrandList = () => {
      const list = document.getElementById('brandListDesktop');
      list.classList.toggle('hidden');
      document.getElementById('brandToggle').textContent = list.classList.contains('hidden') ? '+' : '';
    };

    // ================ Utils ================
    function escapeHtml(str) {
      return String(str).replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;').replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
    }

    window.openProductDetails = (id) => {
      window.location.href = `/productdetails.html?id=${id}`;
    };

    // ================ Init ================
    function initializePage() {
      initializeFilters();
      initializeMobileDropdowns();
      setupEventListeners();
      displayProducts(products);
      updateCategoryUI();
      updatePriceRangeUI();
    }

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initializePage);

    // Scroll to Top Visibility
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      document.querySelector('.go-top-btn').classList.toggle('visible', window.scrollY > 300);
    });

function closeMobileDropdown(type) {
  const dd = document.querySelector(`.filter-dropdown[data-type="${type}"]`);
  if (!dd) return; // Safe!
  const content = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-content');
  const icon = dd.querySelector('.dropdown-header i');
  content.classList.remove('open');
  icon.classList.remove('fa-chevron-up');
  icon.classList.add('fa-chevron-down');
}

Bilkul sahi pakda aapne! chronic.js ke wajah se header nahi chal raha aur main batata hoon kya problem hai aur 100% fix kaise karna hai!

Problem: Header Nahi Chal Raha?

Wajah:

js
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initializePage);

Yeh line initializePage() ko turant chalati hai lekin header abhi load nahi hua hota!

Agar aapka header /header.html se fetch hota hai, toh DOMContentLoaded tabhi fire hota hai jab HTML load ho jata hai lekin fetch() async hota hai!

Solution: Header ke baad chronic.js initialize karo

Step 1: HTML mein chronic.js last mein load karo

html
<!-- Header ke baad -->
<div id="header-placeholder"></div>

<!-- Chronic page content -->
<section class="hero-banner">...</section>

<!-- ... rest of your page ... -->

<!-- chronic.js LAST mein -->
<script src="/Medicine & Healthcare/CHRONIC/chronic.js"></script>

Step 2: chronic.js mein DOMContentLoaded hata do

js
// YE LINE DELETE KARO
// document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initializePage);

Step 3: initializePage() ko manually call karo header load hone ke baad

Agar aapka header.js mein initializeHeader() hai:

js
// header.js ke andar (ya header.html ke baad)
function initializeHeader() {
  // header logic...

  // Chronic page ke liye
  if (window.initializeChronicPage) {
    window.initializeChronicPage();
  }
}

Step 4: chronic.js mein initializePage ko global banao

js
// chronic.js ke end mein
window.initializeChronicPage = function() {
  initializeFilters();
  displayProducts(products);
  updateCategoryUI();
  updatePriceRangeUI();
  initializeMobileDropdowns();
  setupEventListeners();

  // Scroll to top
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const btn = document.querySelector('.go-top-btn');
    if (btn) btn.classList.toggle('visible', window.scrollY > 300);
  });
};

// Ab chronic.js load hone ke baad initialize nahi hoga  header karega!

Final Structure (Working Order)

html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <!-- other CDNs -->
</head>
<body>

  <!-- 1. Header placeholder -->
  <div id="header-placeholder"></div>

  <!-- 2. Chronic page content -->
  <section class="hero-banner">...</section>
  <div class="container mx-auto">...</div>

  <!-- 3. Scripts -->
  <script>
    // Header load karo
    fetch('/header.html')
      .then(r => r.text())
      .then(html => {
        document.getElementById('header-placeholder').innerHTML = html;
        
        // Header JS load karo (agar alag hai)
        const script = document.createElement('script');
        script.src = '/header.js';
        document.body.appendChild(script);
      });
  </script>

  <!-- 4. Chronic JS (last mein) -->
  <script src="/Medicine & Healthcare/CHRONIC/chronic.js"></script>

</body>
</html>

header.js (Example)

js
// header.js
function initializeHeader() {
  console.log("Header loaded");

  // Agar chronic page hai, toh usko initialize karo
  if (typeof window.initializeChronicPage === 'function') {
    window.initializeChronicPage();
  }
}

// Header ready hone ke baad call karo
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  setTimeout(initializeHeader, 100); // fetch ke baad
});
